## 🧅 What O.N.I.O.N Means

The acronym describes how the system works in ways that are understandable to both technical teams and children.

| Letter | System Meaning | Kid-Friendly Meaning | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| **O** | Observe / Origin | 👀 Look | Collect safe inputs and establish trusted origin |
| **N** | Notice / Navigate | 🔎 Notice | Detect patterns, anomalies, and risk signals |
| **I** | Infer / Imagine | 🤔 Think | Reason carefully and choose safe options |
| **O** | Operate / Organize | ✅ Do | Apply policy, enforce constraints, and act safely |
| **N** | Narrate / Notify | 📢 Tell | Explain decisions and notify the right people |

**Kid version:** **Look → Notice → Think → Do → Tell**

